School Info
66	Description	Teach in North Africa links Christian educators with educational opportunities in North Africa for the growth of God's Kingdom. Our school currently has about 115 students from preschool through sixth grade and is growing rapidly! We believe that education, respect for nationals, and the commitment of qualified teachers like you will shape the future leaders and influencers of North Africa!
